price: 26. (Alle) baana iska leh waxa ku sugan samooyinka iyo arlada, kulligood Isagay3 u hoggaansan yihiin (oo adeecaan).
arabic: وَلَهُۥ مَن فِي ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلۡأَرۡضِۖ كُلّٞ لَّهُۥ قَٰنِتُونَ

version.title: Somali translation - Jacob
version.description: Translation of the meanings of the Noble Qur'an into the Somali language, translated by Abdullah Hasan Jacob.
